<view class="page safe-bottom">
  <view class="card review-head" wx:if="{{record}}">
    <text class="eyebrow">OPEN RESULT</text>
    <text class="h1">{{record.icon}} {{record.name}}</text>
    <text class="muted">这次差点花 ¥{{record.amountText}}。选一个结果就好，不用写长篇复盘。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card section" wx:if="{{record}}">
    <text class="h2">开奖时间</text>
    <view class="choice-list">
      <button class="choice {{decision === 'kept' ? 'active' : ''}}" bindtap="selectDecision" data-decision="kept">
        <text class="choice-title">忍住了，省下这笔</text>
        <text class="choice-copy">马上生成一张可以分享的省钱战报。</text>
      </button>
      <button class="choice {{decision === 'bought' ? 'active' : ''}}" bindtap="selectDecision" data-decision="bought">
        <text class="choice-title">还是买了，也没关系</text>
        <text class="choice-copy">诚实记录，下次系统会更懂你的冲动。</text>
      </button>
    </view>

    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">可选：一句原因</text>
      <textarea class="textarea" placeholder="例：我只是太累了，想奖励自己一下。" value="{{reviewText}}" bindinput="onTextInput" maxlength="160" />
    </view>

    <button class="primary-btn submit" bindtap="submitReview">生成战报</button>
    <button class="secondary-btn extend" bindtap="extendCooling">还想等等，再放 3 天</button>
  </view>

  <view class="notice section">
    <text>正式版会把开奖做成留存入口：提醒、周报和分享图都基于这里，但 MVP 先保证用户轻松看懂、轻松记录。</text>
  </view>
</view>
